    '{ "getMore": { "$numberLong": "538" }, "collection": "sp_coll", "batchSize": 3 }',
    3);
 page_num | batch_count | cursor_type | persist_conn 
----------+-------------+-------------+--------------
        1 |           3 |             | t
        2 |           3 |             | t
        3 |           3 |             | t
        4 |           3 |             | t
