-- ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
-- Test G3: Descending sort on single-key ASC index (backward scan, no filter)
-- sort: { a: -1 }, hint: idx_order_a_asc
-- Should produce same ordering as G2 (backward scan on ascending index)
-- ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
